1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/06/surface-pro-11-2.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"what-39-s-great-about-microsoft-39-s-surface-pro-11\"\u003e\n                        What\u0026#39;s great about Microsoft\u0026#39;s Surface Pro 11?\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/surface-pro-11-5g-10.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/surface-pro-11-5g-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/surface-pro-11-5g-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/surface-pro-11-5g-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/surface-pro-11-5g-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/surface-pro-11-5g-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/surface-pro-11-5g-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/surface-pro-11-5g-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/surface-pro-11-5g-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"6000\" height=\"4000\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Surface Pro 11 5G-10\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/surface-pro-11-5g-10.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/surface-pro-11-5g-10.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Surface Pro is one of those unique devices that really manages to deliver when it comes to impressive power in a compact size. This particular model comes with a beautiful and vibrant 13-inch OLED screen, along with a powerful Qualcomm Snapdragon X Elite chip that\u0026#39;s paired with 16GB of RAM and 512GB of internal SSD storage. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eIn \u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/surface-pro-11-review/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eour testing\u003c/a\u003e, we found that this model delivered great performance while also having excellent battery life. This Surface Pro also features one of the best displays so far, and the 65W fast charging is also great to have if you\u0026#39;re trying to charge quickly while on the go. Connectivity is also quite good, with two Thunderbolt 4 and a Surface Connect port. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eIn addition, the Surface Pro 11 supports Wi-Fi 7 and Bluetooth 5.4. You also get a 5MP + IR camera on the front, and there\u0026#39;s a 10MP camera in the rear. If you really want to take the Surface Pro to a new level, we recommend \u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/why-cant-anyone-make-great-detachable-keyboard/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003egrabbing the Flex Keyboard\u003c/a\u003e and stylus. For the most part, this is a really great piece of hardware and at a fantastic price. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                                            \n\n\n\n\n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
